#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Gilānavagga"
msgstr "2. Sick"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Nibbidāsutta"
msgstr "20. Disillusionment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.20:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya "
"nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, "
"lead solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, "
"awakening, and extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn46.20:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.20:1.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.20:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya "
"virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, lead solely to "
"disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and "
"extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.20:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.20:1.6"
msgid "Gilānavaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.1"
msgid "Pāṇā sūriyūpamā dve,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.2"
msgid "gilānā apare tayo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.3"
msgid "Pāraṅgāmī viraddho ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn46.20:2.4"
msgid "ariyo nibbidāya cāti."
msgstr ""
